title: BONUS: NFL All Pro Minnesota Vikings' Kyle Rudolph Sips Bourbon With Fred
itunes:title: BONUS: NFL All Pro Minnesota Vikings' Kyle Rudolph Sips Bourbon With Fred
description:
Kyle Rudolph is one of the best tight ends in the game and is an even better person. When, through a mutual friend, Fred found out Kyle was a bourbon fan, he made sure to connect and sip some whiskey! The pair enjoyed tastes of Weller Full Proof, Four Roses 2014 Single Barrel, Barrel Bourbon Gray Label 15 year and more while talking football, life in the Twin Cities, protecting your best bottles and more.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
